

=Description=

"Bloom is a social and mobilization network for regenerative culture. We host on-the-ground events in cities across the world, and interactive online media. Bloom is a place to find and share practices for whole community health.

These efforts prepare a global network of communities to buffer the coming impacts from Climate Change and a rapidly transforming economic landscape. We take an artistic, creative approach, connecting the solutions that exist now and helping them reach a larger audience."
(http://www.bloomnetwork.org/)

